title: Phil Yeh - The Winged Tiger
description:
The Winged Tiger

International Humor Advisory Council, 1993, 97 pages

Written and Illustrated by Phil Yeh

Introduction by Moebius and Wendy Pini

The introduction is one page of art from each of them. :) 

Surreal and wordless tale of the Winged Tiger as he flies thoughout the world, observing all he finds along the way. Also features Patrick and Rachel Rabbit
